{"tid":2182120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗爭社工籌330萬 今衝刺","createTime":"2020-08-31T05:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T09:36:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca6dd0e8494d9d614cad0eb337a4ce3c3875ee3","tid":2182120,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/GMU3U42EKFBPJO6ZRP2KGQMSGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FGMU3U42EKFBPJO6ZRP2KGQMSGE%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=71bc0dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FGMU3U42EKFBPJO6ZRP2KGQMSGE%2F&h=d1e4367b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/GMU3U42EKFBPJO6ZRP2KGQMSGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n抗爭社工籌330萬 今衝刺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZoFw-WwfdampB8EYB8XpEs4IZb0=/1040x701/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O2KQ4JI3YNGPFMEZQ2VEXPS4E4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZoFw-WwfdampB8EYB8XpEs4IZb0%3D%2F1040x701%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO2KQ4JI3YNGPFMEZQ2VEXPS4E4.JPG&h=60a0aa3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■六名被控社工眾籌訴訟費，截至昨晚11時已籌得近九成款項。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六名社工在反送中運動中因守護抗爭者人權，被警方拘捕控告，面對巨大壓力及沉重訴訟開支。社工發起「撐社工。守護公義」眾籌行動，目標籌集330萬訴訟費，至昨日籌得近290萬。今日是眾籌最後一天，社工期望公眾熱心支援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至今籌得九成訟費<br />\n<br />\n被檢控社工包括五位社總陣地社工和一位社工復興運動社工，於過去一年在抗爭現場捍衞人權和守護生命，因此受到不同程度。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n發起眾籌的社工指出，。。。。。。。。。。。。我還會以社工身份到現場進行人道支援工作嗎？結果每次答案也是一樣。縱使喜歡吃喝玩樂和做社工的我，面對越來越困難去守護公義的局勢，作為社工是無法放棄捍衞人權，放棄守護生命免受傷害」。熱心人士可參考以下網址：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/battlefieldswfunding01/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fbattlefieldswfunding01%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=9e73b087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/battlefieldswfunding01/</a>"},{"pid":"4bef814e78d7b0c597707a30b3ba17486867c8cf","tid":2182120,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捐左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c567a52d04361ca1ef1f12e703ff1cf0db17fa","tid":2182120,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a00332e6b59d416fe09b327d5cc62e9c7bd0bfb","tid":2182120,"uid":323373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"2dde21233e921c7b5daa2899d030edbef0d68a4f","tid":2182120,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c808b714c2848043d5889933843b50cfa41bc5a","tid":2182120,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 